OL,6,Fshould be illegal in England and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, children's doctor
OL,8,Fhave said, claiming current laws are
OL,9,F"unjust" and "dangerously vague".
OL,11,FThe current law in England and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland has created "grey
OL,13,Fareas" which mean there is sometimes a
OL,14,Fdefence to physical punishment, the
OL,15,FRoyal College of Paediatrics and Child
OL,16,FHealth (RCPCH) said.
OL,18,F, including smacking, hitting,
OL,19,Fslapping and shaking, illegal in March
OL,20,F2022, while Scotland introduced a
OL,21,Fsimilar ban in November 2020.
