OL,4,Cin England and Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe RCPCH said amendments to the
OL,7,FChildren Act 2004 for England and the
OL,8,FLaw Reform Order 2006 for Northern
OL,9,FIreland "to remove the 'reasonable
OL,10,Fpunishment' defence from all UK law
OL,11,Fare long overdue".
OL,13,FIts report on the issue argued that,
OL,14,Fahead of a general election, this was
OL,15,Fa time for all political parties to
OL,16,F"make meaningful commitments on this
OL,17,Fimportant children's rights issue".
