OL,6,FWhen pushed on why smacking is legal
OL,7,Fin England, Ms Trott said: "Because we
OL,8,Fthink we have the right balance and
OL,9,Fthe right framework in place, but this
OL,10,Fis something we should always keep
OL,11,Flooking at and the evidence that is
OL,12,Fpresented to us.
OL,14,F"But the evidence thus far is that our
OL,15,Fframework works and is effective, but
OL,16,Fwe should always look at that if more
OL,17,Fevidence comes to light."
OL,19,FLabour said they wanted to "end
OL,20,Fsmacking of children".
