OL,3,CDoctors call for smacking to be banned
OL,4,Cin England and Northern Ireland
OL,6,FProfessor Andrew Rowland, a consultant
OL,7,Fpaediatrician and RCPCH officer for
OL,8,Fchild protection, said physical
OL,9,Fpunishment could also result in a
OL,10,Fchild having the learned belief that
OL,11,Fviolence was accepted and this could
OL,12,F"lead to further instances of violence
OL,13,Fand harm later in life".
OL,15,F"The laws around physical punishment
OL,16,Fas they stand are unjust and
OL,17,Fdangerously vague," Prof Rowland said.
OL,19,F"They create a grey area in which some
OL,20,Fforms of physical punishment may be
OL,21,Flawful, and some are not."
