OL,6,FHe said he was "regularly faced with
OL,7,Fsituations where it is alleged that
OL,8,Fphysical punishment has been used
OL,9,Fagainst a child" but that the "vague
OL,10,Fnature of the laws make it extremely
OL,11,Fchallenging" to talk to families about
OL,12,Fwhat the rules are and therefore more
OL,13,Fdifficult to talk about the best
OL,14,Finterests of their children.
OL,16,FHe added: "This lack of legislative
OL,17,Fclarity can even add an extra layer of
OL,18,Fcomplexity when trying to identify
OL,19,Fcases of child abuse."
